body.description: At Medela Baby we know pacifiers can comfort your little one during the day and at sleep time. With the Day & Night set, you have a dedicated pacifier for both moments at hand. Both are gentle on skin and loved by nine out of ten babies! The Night pacifier has a glow-in-the-dark design that allows you and your little one to find it in the dark. Our pacifiers are designed and produced according to high safety and quality standards. So nothing comes between you two - but love. Set includes 1 Day and 1 Night pacifier.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: At Medela... We believe that nothing is as precious as the bond between mother and baby. Nurturing this special bond is what has inspired us to create Medela Baby, our new baby care category - combining over 60 years of breastfeeding innovation with more than 30 years of scientific research on the natural suckling behavior of breastfed babies, to bring you a range of expertly-designed pacifiers for every stage of your baby’s development. Medela Baby - Day & Night Pacifier Set Medela Baby - Day & Night Pacifier Set The perfect 24-hour set with one ORIGINAL pacifier and one NIGHT pacifier, which glows in the dark. While delivering a soft, lightweight, gentle-on-skin feeling that will make them perfect for your little one, our pacifiers are designed and produced according to high safety and quality standards. So nothing comes between you two - but love. Orthodontic & ergonomic design Glow in the dark Gentle-on-skin SensoPearls Lightweight Includes a protection cap to keep pacifier clean

Features & Benefits Orthodontic Flat symmetric teat for free tongue movement and thin shaft minimizes space between upper and lower jaw. Glow in the dark Easy for you and your baby to find, even when they lights are out. Best of all, it’s designed without a ring so your little one’s sleep isn’t disturbed if he or she moves overnight. Gentle on the skin With SensoPearls to enhance the airflow between your baby's sensitive skin and the pacifier shield.

Light & ergonomic shape Less stress on orofacial musculature and ergonomic shape to smell mom's comforting scent easier. Made without BPA and BPS Developed with experts and made with love in Switzerland. Protection cap Easy to keep pacifier clean and for safe transport.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Tried them all, this is my LO favorite
reviews.reviewText: My baby started on MAM pacifiers which worked great, until I needed to move him to the next size up. The mouth piece was too large for his mouth and a different, more bulb-like shape. He suddenly stopped taking the pacifier, which is a must for him to fall asleep.I saw ads for the Medela pacifier and I figured I’d see how he responded to that mouth piece since it looked more like the 0-6 MAM. He took right to it! The handle on the pacifier is also helpful because he has an easier time grasping it to get it in his mouth.My favorite part tho is how easy it is to connect to a pacifier clip. The MAM I had to thread through the side, which the loop of the clip that attached to the pacifier, pressed against his face. This loops so easily through the handle of the day pacifier and even the nub of the night pacifier has a hole to loop the clip through.The pacifier has a case that covers the mouth piece which is good for throwing in the diaper bag.The design on this is really cute and and it’s much nicer quality, the design does not appear like it will wear off like most decorative pacifiers.Sooo happy to find pacifier for my LO age that he happily took to.
